<h2>Welcome to the KingdomVR metaverse</h2>
<p>
Chat with other users, race motorcycles against them, or build in your own personal world.
</p>
<p>
KingdomVR is almost completely open-source (forked from <a href="https://substrata.info">Substrata</a>), check out the source code <a href="https://github.com/kingdomvr/kingdomvr">on GitHub here</a>.
</p>



