<h2 id="downloads">Downloads</h2>
<p>You can enter <a href="/webclient">KingdomVR in your browser</a>.  Alternatively, explore Substrata with the faster native client by downloading it below.</p>
<p>Windows - Download the official <a href="https://github.com/KingdomVR/launcher/releases/download/v1.0/KingdomVR-Launcher-Installer.exe">KingdomVR Launcher for Windows</a></p>
<p>MacOS and Linux - Download the Substrata client from <a href="https://substrata.info/#downloads">here</a>.</p>

